quran[20{c,v,t}:
15,32,Qaala yaaa Ibleesu maa laka allaa takoona ma'as saajideen
15,33,Qaala lam akul li asjuda libasharin khalaqtahoo min salsaalim min hama im masnoon
15,34,Qaala fakhruj minhaa fa innaka rajeem
15,35,Wa inna 'alikal la'nata ilaa Yawmid Deen
15,36,Qaala Rabbi fa anzirneee ilaa Yawmi yub'asoon
15,37,Qaala fa innaka minal munzareen
15,38,Ilaa Yawmil waqtil ma'loom
15,39,Qaala Rabbi bimaaa aghwaitanee la uzayyinaana lahum fil ardi wa la ughwiyan nahum ajma'een
15,40,Illaa 'ibaadaka minhumul mukhlaseen
15,41,Qaala haaza Siraatun 'alaiya Mustaqeem
15,42,Inna 'ibaadee laisa laka 'alaihim sultaanun illaa manittaba'aka minal ghaaween
15,43,Wa inna jahannama lamaw'iduhum ajma'een
15,44,Lahaa sab'atu abwaab; likulli baabim minhum juz'um maqsoom (section 3)
15,45,Innal muttaqeena fee Jannaatinw wa 'uyoon
15,46,Udkhuloohaa bisalaamin aamineen
15,47,Wa naza'naa ma fee sudoorihim min ghillin ikhwaanan 'alaa sururim mutaqaabileen
15,48,Laa yamas suhum feehaa nasabunw wa maa hum minhaa bimukhrajeen
15,49,Nabbi' 'ibaadeee annneee anal Ghafoorur Raheem
15,50,Wa anna 'azaabee uwal 'azaabul aleem
15,51,Wa nabbi'hum 'an daifi Ibraaheem
